*Sljedeći* dan došao je i on. (The following day he came too.)

Otišao je *sljedeće* godine. (He left the following year.)

Kada se vratio, dala mu je *sljedeću* poruku. (When he returned, she gave him the following message.)

*Sljedećim* putem odlučio je da ide. (He decided to go by the following route.)

Krenuo je *sljedećim* danom. (He started the following day.)